OL,3,CTwo Coventry men jailed for plot to
OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,FTwo men from Coventry has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor a combined 24-and-a-half years in
OL,8,Fprison for their plot to pick up a #4m
OL,9,Fcocaine haul.
OL,11,F39-year-old Richard Farmer was
OL,12,Farrested when he drove to the light
OL,13,Faircraft which had landed at
OL,14,FDeenethorpe Airfield in Corby in
OL,15,FNorthamptonshire, on February 23rd,
OL,16,F2022.
OL,18,FA black wheeled suitcase was brought
OL,19,Ffrom the plane and placed into
OL,20,FFarmer's car at the edge of the runway.
