OL,3,CTwo Coventry men jailed for plot to
OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,FWhen Farmer exited the airfield, the
OL,7,Fcar was stopped by officers from
OL,8,FNorthamptonshire police and 50 brown
OL,9,Ftaped packages were found within the
OL,10,Fsuitcase.
OL,12,FThe drugs, which weighed 50kg, had a
OL,13,Fstreet value of #4 million.
OL,15,FWhen officers examined Farmer's phone,
OL,16,Fthey found incriminating evidence
OL,17,Flinking him to co-conspirator 39-year-
OL,18,Fold Blaine Harvey.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
