OL,3,CTwo Coventry men jailed for plot to
OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,FThe pair had been in regular contact
OL,7,Fand Harvey appeared to be waiting away
OL,8,Ffrom the airfield to meet Farmer after
OL,9,Fthe cocaine had been collected.
OL,11,FInvestigators established that Harvey
OL,12,Fwould help Farmer move the drugs
OL,13,Faround various areas including
OL,14,FBedfordshire, Cambridgeshire,
OL,15,FNorthamptonshire, Coventry, Kent and
OL,16,FEssex.
