OL,3,CTwo Coventry men jailed for plot to
OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,FHarvey was arrested at his home on
OL,7,FApril 7th, 2022. Both denied being
OL,8,Fknowingly concerned in the importation
OL,9,Fof 50kg of cocaine but were convicted
OL,10,Fon July 16th 2025, after an eight-day
OL,11,Fat Northampton Crown Court.
OL,13,FThey were sentenced at the same court
OL,14,Fon Friday (July 18th). Farmer was
OL,15,Fsentenced to 12 years in prison and
OL,16,FHarvey was sentenced to 12 years and
OL,17,Fsix months in prison.
OL,19,FThe plane, which had arrived in the UK
OL,20,Ffrom Belgium, continued its journey to
OL,21,FIreland.
