OL,3,CTwo Coventry men jailed for plot to
OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,FOn arrival, three men from Sweden and
OL,7,FLithuania were arrested by the Garda
OL,8,Fand extradited to Sweden where they
OL,9,Fhave since been convicted of drugs
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FNCA Branch Commander, Lydia Bloomfield
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is a significant haul of
OL,14,FClass A drugs brought in on a private
OL,15,Fplane in the hopes of avoiding
OL,16,Fdetection. Farmer and Harvey were
OL,17,Fworking together under an organised
OL,18,Fcrime group to deal them on our
OL,19,Fstreets with little regard for
OL,20,Fanything but their profit.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
