OL,4,Cpick up #4m cocaine haul
OL,6,F"These convictions will disrupt the
OL,7,Fupstream organised crime group behind
OL,8,Fthis smuggling and we will continue to
OL,9,Fwork to stop those who attempt to
OL,10,Fbring drugs into the country from
OL,11,Foverseas.
OL,13,F"With thanks to our policing partners
OL,14,Fin Northamptonshire, Ireland and
OL,15,FSweden, we have taken a large quantity
OL,16,Fof dangerous drugs out of circulation."
